> Indiana Lynx, Fever ready for WNBA Finals-deciding Game 5 Indiana Fever's Tamika Catchings takes questions from the media, Tuesday, Oct. 13, 2015, in Minneapolis as the team prepares for the decisive Game 5 of the WNBA basketball finals against the Minnesota Lynx.
